Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it \Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body \Nturned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew reached the Fish-Man \NIsland located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the New Fish-Man Pirates  who are \Nlooking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after \NShirahoshi, are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats find themselves \Ncaught up in the turmoil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and involved in an all-out war!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Noah is turning away. It's \Nnot gonna crash into the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess-sama saved us \Nby drawing the ship away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Princess Shirahoshi!\N--Please escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go out to the sea in order \Nto keep the Noah away from the bubble!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you one last chance, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say "Yes," I'll spare your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have mercy, Decken-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not my type!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna let her marry a guy like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.99,0:04:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's our only baby sister! We're \Nnot gonna let you hurt her, Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Mamboshi-sama! Brother \NRyuboshi-sama! Hoe-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that we suspected you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it. Take me to the deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hordy Jones!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Neptune? Did you kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tormenting Shirahoshi with the Noah now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Bro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a good idea too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Let me hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you die now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen to this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:06:01.21,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"The Fierce Fight Begins! Luffy vs. Hordy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy! You... squirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My left hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...touched you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, you bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You betrayed me first, Decken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I panicked a little when this \Nship covered up the sky over the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was a good idea to break the bubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fish-Man Island would be washed away
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we'd still have the Fish-Man District.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you die here and now, your Mark-Mark \Npower will become ineffective
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this ship will fall onto \Nthe Fish-Man Island again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it will destroy everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, more than anything, I want all of \Nthose annoying Straw Hats to be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousands of my men will die too
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can just get more human \Nslaves, as many as I like, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousands will die, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good. But first,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...drop dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become a martyr for the New Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the ship will start falling again and \Nit will fall onto the Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm a kind man, I'll \Nmake your dream come true,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the very least I can do, before you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill Shirahoshi for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He stabbed Decken! What kind \Nof relationship do they have?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to think about \Nthat. Hordy's gonna come this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid interlopers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brothers-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi! Get away at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're out of the Hard Shell \NTower - it's so easy to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Merfolk may be the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:11:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fastest swimmers in the world but \NI'm way faster than you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Snake Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama! Brother Fukaboshi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Straw Hat!\N--B-Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to be late. I was \Ncaught up in strategizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.64,0:12:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:08.66,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,CONCHCORDE PLAZA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.02,0:12:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, at Conchcorde Plaza \Non the Fish-Man Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Vander Decken-sama abandoned me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to become a
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sacrifice upon Shirahoshi's \Ndeath, along with the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you fight, Sea Bonze!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Do something about the Kraken!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Beat him up, Kraken!\N--You're strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're both huge but he doesn't \Nseem like he wants to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kraken will defeat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Great Monk! You must have misheard him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What Decken said to you was "I'll \Nleave the plaza up to you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:13:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means he wasn't \Ngonna destroy the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he said "Become a sacrifice."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted you to fight hard as though \Nyou were going to sacrifice yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Isn't that right, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Y-Yeah... he's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How lucky to be trusted \Nby your captain that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're amazing!\N--It's time for you to man up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's what it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, take this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and beat the Straw Hats up with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Energy Steroid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.19,0:13:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. It's not gonna \Nwork on that giant body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's working tremendously well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surume!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Decken! I'm sorry \Nthat I didn't trust you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! He beat the hell out of the Kraken!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What happened? Are you all right?!\N--It's no good! He passed out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys my enemies too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's like a different person!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it all up to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.91,0:15:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is my enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That guy right there, Wadatsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Jimbei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish-Man Karate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7000 Brick...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.31,0:15:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Roundhouse Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could he do such a giant \Ncreature that much damage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! The wind blast brought Nami-san down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Who is it this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You big shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would happen if you \Nso much as make a scratch
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or two on our beautiful navigator?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable! His kick worked too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How strong is his leg that it \Ncan hurt a giant like him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will fight you, Great Monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:17:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay with your life, you Jumbo Steamed Bun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How strong can they get?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mil Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help us, Hyouzou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, can I get a wasabi octopus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're not in a bar! Plus, \Nyou shouldn't eat octopus!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! He's completely drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:17:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can prove yourself now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's your chance to become \Nan officer in one move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew a little surprise \Nattack like this wouldn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the soon-to-be No.1 Fish-Man \Nswordsman - Nuru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's wrong?\N--Is it a hangover?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouzou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you say the same thing after this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't see, you can't \Ndefend yourself from my sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only use your eyes to \Nsee. That's why you're weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go train some more and come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was just dumb luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the No.1 Fish-Man \Nswordsman, I won't lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is No.1?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouzou-san, we're on your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He looks strange.\N--That's not how he gets drunk usually!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's much stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tottering Hash!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shields don't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:21:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was writhing in agony without \Nany injury until a while ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding? This is like what \Nhappened when Hordy-san changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouzou-san has become a monster, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels great! I feel a surge of energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I wanna cut more people!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me cut you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Somebody, stop him! There's \Nno way to defend ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.18,0:21:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hyouzou-san got stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look tougher than the \Nanglerfish I just beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.79,0:22:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.81,0:22:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm gonna take this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.16,0:22:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be a nice warm-up \Nbefore we go to the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.17,0:22:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It gets less powerful in water as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.18,0:22:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Less powerful"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.90,0:22:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid lowly creature!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.03,0:22:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know where you \Nare?! You're in the deep sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.38,0:22:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A human like you has no \Nchance to win a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.31,0:22:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everything will come to an end soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's Shirahoshi or the \NFish-Man Island or your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fool like you can't protect anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.52,0:23:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.12,0:23:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I worked for...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.99,0:23:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...those 2 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.44,0:23:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats are battling the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,officers of the New Fish-Man Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new, stronger attacks the crew has \Nlearned in their two years of training
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,continue to be revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.87,0:23:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Far above them,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.64,0:23:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Noah is getting closer by the second,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.56,0:23:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as it descends to destroy Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.81,0:23:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.40,0:23:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Massive Confused Fight! The Straw \NHats vs. The New Fish-Man Pirates!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.51,0:23:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
